<span id="freeTextContainer13919442327995605046">Forever Red is live! I can&apos;t wait for you all to read it. <br/><br/>Neil and Lia had a much different story than what I usually write. They&apos;re two kids who are lost, each for different reasons, and because of their time together, are able to find themselves. <br/><br/>The characters in this book make me smile. <br/><br/>Happy reading!</span>
  <span id="freeText13919442327995605046" style="display:none">Forever Red is live! I can't wait for you all to read it. <br /><br />Neil and Lia had a much different story than what I usually write. They're two kids who are lost, each for different reasons, and because of their time together, are able to find themselves. <br /><br />The characters in this book make me smile. <br /><br />Happy reading!</span>
